  "notes": "Live Admin GraphQL 2026-04 capture creates a disposable product, records a real Spanish shopLocaleEnable setup response, uses an existing market hydrated through upstreamCalls, proves translationsRegister rejects a non-sentinel fabricated market GID with MARKET_DOES_NOT_EXIST, proves translationsRemove with the fabricated market GID silently no-ops, proves PackingSlipTemplate body rejects market-custom content with RESOURCE_NOT_MARKET_CUSTOMIZABLE, registers market-scoped product title and product_type translations, reads them back through translatableResource(...).translations(locale:, marketId:), removes both requested key x locale x market combinations in one translationsRemove(marketIds:) call, and verifies the market-scoped downstream read is empty after cleanup. Proxy replay earns product and locale state through public GraphQL setup requests rather than hidden state seeding."
